{"tid":799420,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"e^(2x) 係一個複合函數?","createTime":"2018-08-30T05:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T05:48:39.000Z","uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"557724ab3edd7b0fea5606cf3772ef585920c51d","tid":799420,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:12:06.000Z","msg":"因為搵 e^(2x) 時會用到chain rule<br />\n其實e^(2x) 係咪一個複合函數<br />\n如果係既, 複合響邊?<br />\n<br />\nF(x) = sin(cos(tan(x))) &lt;--  依個係複合函數我明<br />\n因為 F(x) = f(g(h(x)))<br />\n但e^(2x)都係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ea0a99208bf725ddb24defe375a443726972d8","tid":799420,"uid":51129,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"557724ab3edd7b0fea5606cf3772ef585920c51d","tid":799420,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:12:06.000Z","msg":"因為搵 e^(2x) 時會用到chain rule<br />\n其實e^(2x) 係咪一個複合函數<br />\n如果係既, 複合響邊?<br />\n<br />\nF(x) = sin(cos(tan(x))) &lt;--  依個係複合函數我明<br />\n因為 F(x) = f(g(h(x)))<br />\n但e^(2x)都係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:22:11.000Z","msg":"f(x) = e^x<br />\ng(x) = 2x<br />\n<br />\ne^(2x) = f(g(x))"},{"pid":"f324a787cb09d5d748ab4b0e5ddcdf51576ceb02","tid":799420,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"Thanks bro~ 明曬~!!!<br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894a818c4f85327e1c20be500523d6161f6d0d85","tid":799420,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:45:20.000Z","ms